PRIESTS; CATHOLIC CHURCH -- EL SALVADOR; EL SALVADOR -- ARMED FORCES; EL 
SALVADOR -- GOVERNMENT; EL SALVADOR -- REVOLTS; DEATH SQUADS; UNITED STATES -- 
