County contest. Andy Koffman, an animal importer, wants to enter his 8-pound 
Goliath frogs in the whimsical contest made famous by Mark Twain. Officials 
aren't sure that's fair to the usual competitors -- common California bullfrogs 
-- which are a fraction of the African creatures' size. Associated Press 
</P>
