<P>
Photo, Night Lights, Big City A man is silhouetted as he walks in front of 
massive illuminated sculpture that welcomes visitors to Arco Plaza in downtown 
Los Angeles. JIM MENDENHALL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA010990-0009 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 159311 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 9, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 5; Column 1; Foreign Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
