POLICE -- EAST GERMANY; INTELLIGENCE SERVICES; REUNIFICATION; DEMONSTRATIONS -- 
EAST GERMANY; EAST GERMANY -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY; NAZIS 
</P>
