<P>
HOUSE FIRE TRACED TO DOG'S ELECTRIC BLANKET 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
TULSA, Okla. 
