<P>
BATTLING THE MEDFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Los Angeles County will conduct aerial spraying of malathion tonight from 9 
p.m. to 3 a.m. 
</P>
<P>
Area: 47 square miles encompassing Boyle Heights, City Terrace, Eagle Rock, El 
Sereno, Elysian Park, Glassell Park, Highland Park, Lincoln Heights, Mt. 
</P>
<P>
Washington, Montecito Heights, Monterey Hills and parts of Alhambra, East Los 
Angeles, Monterey Park and Pasadena. 
</P>
<P>
Precautions: Stay indoors, keep animals indoors, wash animal dishes and toys 
left outside, cover cars, keep doors and windows closed. 
</P>
<P>
Information: Toll-free numbers for the Agricultural Commissioner: (800) 
356-2894; (800) 225-1346. 
</P>
